com.oracle.sfp.scripting.api

Interface IRangeMapAPI<T extends Comparable<? super T>,U>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - source data type of the mapping
    U - target data type of the mapping
    All Superinterfaces:
    Function<T,U>, IScriptingObject

    public interface IRangeMapAPI<T extends Comparable<? super T>,U>
extends Function<T,U>, IScriptingObject
    Helps create a table mapping ranges of source values to given fixed target values.
